content.rendered:
SNAKE PRINT TREND

Hello loves! I love Fall because we get to incorporate lots of prints like leopard print which I love, and classic snake print trend. I have seen a lot of beautiful street style pictures from the 1960s and ’70 with the most beautiful snake print coats, tops, and skirts. Here are my favorite ways to wear this timeless print. Click on the names below to shop.

Snake earrings 

Proenza Bag 

Chloe snake print bucket bag

Alias Mae Boots

Both looks are from FWRD.COM

Very similar snake print skirt but at only $80 from Topshop

Snake print jacket from Topshop at $85

LOVE DIONNE
